# Analysis of Haitian Identity Documents for SNISID

## 1. DCPJ - Certificat de Police (Police Certificate)
- **Institution:** Direction Centrale de la Police Judiciaire (DCPJ) / Bureau de Renseignements Judiciaires (BRJ).
- **Key Fields:** 
  - Certificate Number (at the top, e.g., DCPJ/BRJ/3-CIE/...).
  - Date of Issue and Expiry.
  - Full Name (Monsieur/Madame).
  - Date and Place of Birth.
  - Nationality.
  - National Identification Number (NIN).
  - Physical Description (Taille, Poids, Couleur, Cheveux, Yeux).
  - Digital Formula (Formule Digitale).
  - Signatures of Officials (Resp. de l'Identité Judiciaire, Responsable du BRJ, Directeur Central).
  - Security Features: Official stamps, unique numbering.

## 2. ONI - Carte d'Identification Nationale (CIN)
- **Institution:** Office National d'Identification (ONI).
- **Face Fields:**
  - Card Number (Numéro de carte).
  - First Name (Prénom).
  - Last Name (Nom).
  - Gender (Sexe).
  - Nationality.
  - Date of Birth.
  - Place of Birth (Department, Commune).
  - Date of Issue and Expiry.
  - Unique Identification Number (Numéro d'identification unique).
  - Photo and Signature.
- **Back Fields:**
  - Barcode (PDF417).
  - Machine Readable Zone (MRZ).
  - Address.
  - Serial Number.

## 3. ANH - Extrait de Naissance (Birth Certificate)
- **Institution:** Archives Nationales d'Haïti (ANH).
- **Key Fields:**
  - Act Number (Acte n°).
  - Year, Register, Page.
  - Date of Birth (written in letters and numbers).
  - Full Name of the Child.
  - Parents' Names and details.
  - Official Signature and Stamp.
  - Barcode and unique ID (e.g., A1964829).

## 4. DIE/DGI - Passeport (Passport)
- **Institution:** Direction de l'Immigration et de l'Émigration (DIE) / DGI for payment.
- **Key Fields:**
  - Passport Number.
  - Type, Country Code.
  - Surname and Given Names.
  - Nationality.
  - Date of Birth.
  - Gender.
  - Place of Birth.
  - Date of Issue and Expiry.
  - Personal NIF (Numéro d'Identification Fiscale).
  - Authority (e.g., DIE Bureau Aquin).
  - MRZ at the bottom.
